{
  "stem": "1292.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whereas the camp-- were as a-- we knew that they not somehow doing well in-- on the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some glimpses coming sometime of information from out--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- I think there was even some information that people did hear when the German was discussing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or it maybe came from Goth, because he did have the Jewish cook.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know-- with what's described in the book.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The information did sneak in from different area, but there was some information.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also, as it came to a liquidation of the concentration camp, we heard from distant sound artillery, yes?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then first, we did think it was our imagination.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we did see this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The camp was in liquidation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- At this time--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and then was the-- the list made-- as you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, the people from Emalia did come to Plaszow as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Schindler couldn't stop that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did have to come to the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And not all the people which did work in the Emalia did come-- was put on a list.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because my auntie, the one which is in Montefiore home, she was in Emalia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And yet, she wasn't on the Schindler List.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they was saying, there was a lot of corruption who was on the list and whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I must say, in all honesty, what I know, it wasn't any corruption on my part.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was in-- on the list.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was a-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] There's the door-- the door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was rumors, yes, there was rumors that it's a list made.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is a list made.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody did want to be on the list.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a big havoc.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very chaotic and undisciplined.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
